File: As of midnight motorists will pay nine cents more for both grades of petrol. JOHANNESBUEG - Motorists can brace themselves for another petrol increase. As of midnight motorists will pay nine cents more for both grades of petrol. READ: Petrol price to increase Diesel will cost you 33 cents per litre. Illuminating paraffin will be increasing by 8 cents per litre.. The Department  of Energy says higher oil price during the period as well as an an inclusion of a carbon tax levy were behind the hike.